<p><b>What is advertising in business pdf?</b> Basic of Advertising. Advertising is a paid, non-personal communication through mass media used to persuade consumers about a product, service or idea. It is usually sponsored communication that aims to influence consumers and make them aware of or favorably inclined toward something.</p>
